public class RspObject
extends logical

An RspObject represents an instance a specific RSP class.

RspObject(value=NA, attrs=list(), ...)

Arguments

value

An R object.

attrs

RSP attributes as a named list, e.g. type, language, and source.

...

Additional named RSP attributes.
